item.title: Dadgum Box Scores | Purpose
item.description: Purpose Dadgum box scores is a collection of every UNC men’s basketball box score since the 2003-04 season. Nothing else. Just box scores. Dadgum box scores. Who am I? I’m Chris. I put together this site because I wanted it to be easier to find old UNC box scores. I was tried of navigating crappy sites and not finding what I wanted. It shouldn’t be that hard to find a box score.
